# Converge Plugin Settings

This file configures the Converge Claude Code plugin.

## Fields

- `enabled` (boolean): Master switch to enable/disable the plugin. Default: `true`.
- `daemon_autostart` (boolean): Whether the plugin automatically starts the Converge daemon if not running. Default: `true`.
- `startup_timeout_ms` (integer): Maximum time (in milliseconds) to wait for daemon startup. Default: `10000` (10 seconds).

## Example

```yaml
---
enabled: true
daemon_autostart: true
startup_timeout_ms: 15000
---
```

## Restart Required

After creating or modifying this file, restart Claude Code for changes to take effect.
